data.description: Amazing move in ready, four-bedroom home on beautiful Lady's Island! From the manicured yards, to the immaculate inside, this is a perfectly maintained home! This home features a living area in the front as you enter and a family room in the back with a updated kitchen in the middle. Four comfortable bedrooms with the primary bedroom featuring its own bath. The large screened back porch will be your favorite spot in the house! There is also a large shed in the back. All of this in a ranch style! Hurry!
